stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Operation
    Operation --> Success: No Error
    Operation --> Error: Exception
    
    Error --> Categorize
    Categorize --> Retryable: Transient Error
    Categorize --> NonRetryable: Permanent Error
    
    Retryable --> Retry: Attempts < Max
    Retryable --> Fallback: Attempts >= Max
    Retry --> Operation
    
    NonRetryable --> Log
    Fallback --> Log
    Log --> Notify
    Notify --> Recovery
    
    Recovery --> [*]
    Success --> [*]